C\u00daP QG BRAZIL 2018 - T\u1ee8 K\u1ebeT</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">17/08 05:15</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Palmeiras - Bahia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2419","checkdouble":"194578"},{"date":"07:17 16/08","title":"Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/rohit-chand-cau-thu-nepal-ma-olympic-viet-nam-phai-de-chung-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Persija Jakarta, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rohit Chand \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Indonesia y\u00eau m\u1ebfn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3m s\u00e1t n\u00e0o di\u1ec5n ra trong m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Olympic Nepal. D\u00f9 ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng v\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rohit Chand. 90 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti, Chand ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con thoi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Rohit-Chand,-cau-thu-Nepal-ma-Olympic-Viet-Nam-phai-de-chung-nhat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rohit Chand c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t, Chand n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e1u l\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi r\u1ea5t th\u00f4ng minh. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt c\u1ee7a Chand c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u phen b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gyotoku Koji mang t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Chand l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i cho tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009 khi m\u1edbi tr\u00f2n 16 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Chand \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 46 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 n\u1eafm chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3. Trong l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Persija v\u1eabn h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i ASIAD nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb b\u1edfi \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, Nepal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. V\u00e0 thay v\u00ec s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m&quot;, Rohit Chand cho hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n &quot;h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi&quot;. Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kiran Limbu v\u00e0 Chand l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1. Chand c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3, anh t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng Persija \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup. Khi \u1ea5y, Chand \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00f2a c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/rohit-chand-persija-jakarta1crdkuqysjz4h138rr2d6hcrvk-1534310271134439729055.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n Chand mang l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang-seo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf m\u00e0 lan sang kh\u1eafp b\u1ed1n kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o, Chand r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn, sau m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c tr\u00e1i tim.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChand l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Persija Jakarte t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5y, b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nepal \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2y s\u0103n \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 FC Viking \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Chand \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt fans h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a AFC v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia, d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u01b0 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh g\u1eafn k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Chand v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Persija. N\u0103m 2017, anh tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 &quot;nh\u00e0&quot; tr\u01b0\u1edbc ni\u1ec1m h\u00e2n hoan c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y 14/8, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Persija l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Java \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp l\u1eeda cho Nepal. &quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m k\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng Jakmania (t\u00ean g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a fan h\u1eadm m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Persija) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho Nepal v\u00e0 t\u00f4i&quot;, Chand tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-myanmar-suyt-danh-bai-chdcnd-trieu-tien-tai-asiad-2018-472-194574.html\">Olympic Myanmar su\u00fdt \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/chu-nha-olympic-indonesia-bat-ngo-thua-bai-tuong-cua-olympic-viet-nam-472-194562.html\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/ngoi-sao-son-heung-min-du-bi-olympic-han-quoc-van-thang-tennis-o-asiad-2018-472-194561.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn th\u1eafng tennis \u1edf Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-malaysia-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-o-asiad-18-472-194553.html\">Olympic Malaysia kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 \u1edf Asiad 18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport5.vn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2418","checkdouble":"194579"},{"date":"07:32 16/08","title":"B\u1ea3ng vinh danh Thibaut Courtois b\u1ecb C\u0110V Atletico Madrid ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bang-vinh-danh-thibaut-courtois-bi-pha-hoai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bangladesh-vs-Thai-Lan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>\u00a0</span>U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain: 1-4<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\u1ede b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018,\u00a0U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng khi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Bangladesh d\u00f9 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Qatar thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f2n t\u00edch l\u0169y ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i mang ra so \u0111\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o U23 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/bxh-bangb-asiad-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2417","checkdouble":"194580"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>Ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal,-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea7y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c v\u00e0 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Nepal t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb,&nbsp;m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 \u1edf Bangladesh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, Olympic Nepal v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014. Nh\u1eefng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Nepal v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u1ea5y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 15/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay c\u1ea3 khi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 tin trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Olympic Nepal. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hai nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3 ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t trong hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u1edf trung t\u00e2m tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1p m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nepal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Nepal \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, NHM Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: 3-0</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan: Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2416","checkdouble":"194581"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi &quot;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin&quot; b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 t\u1ea1i Villas Peros v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 8-0, \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Villas Peros, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u00edn t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CR7 nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ronaldo, tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci hay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Serie A 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. M\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 Marc'Antonio Bentegodi b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi Juventus h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chievo Verona.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2415","checkdouble":"194582"},{"date":"07:48 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-u23-bangladesh-vs-u23-thai-lan-16h00-ngay-168-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bangladesh-vs-Thai-Lan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>\u00a0</span>U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain: 1-4<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\u1ede b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018,\u00a0U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng khi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Bangladesh d\u00f9 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Qatar thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f2n t\u00edch l\u0169y ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i mang ra so \u0111\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o U23 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/bxh-bangb-asiad-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2414","checkdouble":"194583"}]}